{"tid":1543281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[中/Eng]齊認識監警會/What is IPCC?","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:12:06.000Z","uid":68445,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b0cdd17d52d47bb6a9f3331e41448d7ff53de122","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"大家都聽過哂可能，但外國好多人唔知佢有幾廢，幫幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Background:</span></strong></span><br />\n監警會是根據《獨立監察警方處理投訴委員會條例》（《監警會條例》）（香港法例第604章）成立的獨立機構，其職能是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">觀察</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">監察</span></strong>和<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">覆檢</span></strong>警務處處長就須匯報投訴的處理和調查工作。<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nThe Independent Police Complaints Council (IPCC) is an independent body established under the Independent Police Complaints Council Ordinance (IPCCO) (Cap. 604, Laws of Hong Kong) to <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">observe</span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">monitor</span></strong> and <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">review</span></strong> the handling and investigation of Reportable Complaints against the Police by the Commissioner of Police.<br />\n============================================================<br />\n監警會主席梁定邦表示，警務處處長及特首承諾配合他們的工作，將提供所有需要的資料。然而，他同時承認，專案組<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有權力</span></strong>傳召證人或蒐集證據。可見，他們只能「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">審視</span></strong>」而非「調查」警隊行動；而最終監警會的報告能夠有多深入和全面，非常<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">視乎警方提供多少資料。</span></strong><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nAnthony Neoh, the chairman of IPCC, admitted that the council has <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">NO AUTHORITY</span></strong> in summoning witnesses or collecting evidences. They can <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">only review,</span></strong> but not &quot;investigate&quot; the work of Hong Kong Police. The depth and coverage of the IPCC review report fully <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">depends on how much information can be provided by the Hong Kong Police.</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9345ec83a9a61f9c913b3c1d0f5ea0e9bde72d18","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:36:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">指控成功率/Allegations results</span></strong></span>(extracted from 17/18 annual report)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8V58vVH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8V58vVH.png&h=0787f1de&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">**証明屬實率/Substantial rate: 68/2872=0.02%</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">無法追查/Not persuable : 47.9% </span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a5hF6Cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa5hF6Cf.png&h=a772217e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRs3jXs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRs3jXs.png&h=183737df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>果陣仲未咁/the report was even issued before all these..:</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMZdHd1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMZdHd1.png&h=053283ea&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cra4OT1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcra4OT1.png&h=201bd8b6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y6Jufy2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy6Jufy2.png&h=d9b636a8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n============================================================<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">指控到又如何/Even substantiated, then?</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bmnbtJb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbmnbtJb.png&h=e344d630&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n獨立監察警方處理投訴委員會（監警會）自2009年6月成立以來，每年均收到數千宗投訴警員的個案。有報道指，當中只有約3%至4%個案獲證明屬實。懲處方面，9年來只有1名警員被<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">刑事檢控</span></strong>，大部分警員只接受警告或訓諭。濫用武力指控方面，由2011/12至2017/18年度，有逾2000項投訴<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警察毆打</strong></span>的指控，當中僅2項指控屬實，成功率得0.09%。<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nSince the incorporation from June 2009, thousands of allegation had been received from IPCC every year. Only 3-4% of the allegations were reported as substantiated. For the punishment, only 1 police officer out of all was ever under <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>criminal proceeding</strong></span> in 9 years, others were getting verbal warnings or advice. For <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Assault</strong></span> cases, there were above 2000 cases in 9 years, only 2 of them were reported as substantiated, the success rate is 0.09%.<br />\n<br />\n===========================================================<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">成員/Composition:</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gkSSdoq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgkSSdoq.png&h=b99cb47a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTYmQ94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTYmQ94.png&h=50abc949&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMcCpu4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMcCpu4.png&h=f87e80b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUEJj3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUEJj3q.png&h=49373865&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nIn general, most of the members, even those vice-chairs in IPCC, their identity, their relationship with the Pro-Beijing camp, their donations to the HK police force and even their public speech undoubtedly shows that they are on the side of the Hong Kong Police.<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.giphy.com/media/JTOg4NWMkXDsWMGeSy/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FJTOg4NWMkXDsWMGeSy%2Fgiphy.gif&h=5a8ae108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.giphy.com/media/dUCaettZNeUfe2QG3m/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FdUCaettZNeUfe2QG3m%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c6adfc09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\nFive Demands, not one less.</span></span>"},{"pid":"9193c2d6742c3cc22be18853a211d998e6827fac","tid":1543281,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"042119e598720fa985f10c1beef71e92290b0fea","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"連豬1推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ad15f1d56dff22ea56b5079b1e59cdefd599ed","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:41:24.000Z","msg":"連豬2推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bee0e5f8c77e02e9ae8d7d7bf26b8bf8fa175b1","tid":1543281,"uid":32187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"整小冊子派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9dfec58ec47360e3d18d4f945ec66163001729","tid":1543281,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80e0a8be0da9cde522d2290422509ddf69e2b5f","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bee0e5f8c77e02e9ae8d7d7bf26b8bf8fa175b1","tid":1543281,"uid":32187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"整小冊子派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:43:52.000Z","msg":"我都覺得有啲長，已經縮減咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6300c02785f8c9e1320f23ea77e6a547cbd679c4","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"民主黨接獲上水街坊鍾先生投訴，指警員濫用私刑，在北區醫院病房內虐打手腳被綁病床的62歲鍾父。虐打案發生於6月底、事主兒子於6月27日已經向投訴警察課投訴，事隔近兩個月，仍未有進展，直至事主兒子開記者會，播出所取得的醫管局閉路電視影片後，警方才拘捕涉案警員。謝振中解釋，警方昨日才首次見到醫管局閉路電視錄影，認為事態嚴重，遂作出拘捕。<br />\n謝振中又說，「喺醫院病房裡面，我哋一貫理解係無CCTV，所以當刻同事認為無呢，就無進行相關嘅調查。」"},{"pid":"939d1fce92eb1b12ffae67739c9e674f3bf4d0e7","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Oq12Qho.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOq12Qho.gif&h=af1b8ca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWe don't forget, we don't forgive."},{"pid":"79a888b486c6dd3267cc813153ee2d274089eab5","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"連豬3連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c9c10d8f3fba8b355dae246922307979f95693","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:54:01.000Z","msg":"4推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686cb3b25cff463f0eebb75f08eb814be70fbfec","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"5連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd98881db4c86c714e6a87e9149158b7ad4ba9f","tid":1543281,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"6連pish<img src=